            "text": "Implementation Best Practices"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "For production deployment of the Nanonets OCR S api, use asynchronous processing for large batches. Implement robust error handling for timeouts and invalid inputs. Cache results for repeated requests to enhance performance. Monitor usage to avoid rate limiting."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Troubleshooting and Optimization"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Address low accuracy by preprocessing images: ensure high resolution, proper alignment, and noise reduction. Check API responses for error codes like 400 for bad requests or 401 for authentication issues. Refer to the official documentation for detailed error resolution."
